01/08/2003
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- The BiH State Border Service arrested an Egyptian citizen believed to be a member of the al-Islamiyyah terrorist organisation.
Security officers detained the suspect, his wife, three children and a driver at the Orasje border crossing Wednesday (30 July).
The driver is a BiH citizen, who received money to take his family to Slovenia.
Officials found forged passports issued in Belgium.
(FTV, BBC - 31/07/03)
